    "Description": "\u003e [!WARNING]\r\n\u003e Warning this release introduces a regression that break cli autocompletion.\r\n\u003e More information on https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/issues/9028\r\n\u003e Fixed in [v0.118.0](https://www.updatecli.io/changelogs/updatecli/changelogs/v0.118.0/) \r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n## 🐛 Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- fix(autodiscovery/kubernetes): handle empty yaml @olblak (#8943)\r\n- fix(dockerdigest): include HideTag in ReportConfig to prevent source cache collision @max-chaban (#8927)\r\n- fix: sanitize version when checking the latest Updatecli version available @olblak (#8824)\r\n\r\n## 🧰 Maintenance\r\n\r\n- chore(deps): bump github.com/containerd/containerd from 1.7.30 to 1.7.32 in the go_modules group across 1 directory @[dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot) (#8959)\r\n- chore(deps): bump github.com/go-git/go-git/v5 from 5.19.0 to 5.19.1 in the go_modules group across 1 directory @[dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot) (#8936)\r\n- deps(go): bump module code.gitea.io/sdk/gitea to v0.25.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8932)\r\n- deps(go): bump module golang.org/x/mod to v0.36.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8934)\r\n- chore: Improve version update message warning @olblak (#8928)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/moby/buildkit to v0.30.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8908)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/service/ec2 to v1.302.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8911)\r\n- chore(ci): upgrade uv version @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8899)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/getsops/sops/v3 to v3.13.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8892)\r\n- deps(go): bump module golang.org/x/net to v0.54.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8885)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/minamijoyo/hcledit to v0.2.18 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8875)\r\n- deps(go): bump module helm.sh/helm/v3 to v3.21.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8860)\r\n- deps(go): bump module github.com/fluxcd/source-controller/api to v1.8.4 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8851)\r\n- chore: add ci pipeline job in global report @olblak (#8825)\r\n- deps(go): bump module gopkg.in/ini.v1 to v1.67.2 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8808)\r\n- chore(dockerfile): upgrade node version @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#8777)\r\n- chore: update pnpm/action-setup version in workflows @olblak (#8748)\r\n\r\n## 📝 Documentation\r\n\r\n- fix: convert README.adoc to markdown @olblak (#8954)\r\n\r\n## Contributors\r\n\r\n@dependabot[bot], @max-chaban, @olblak, @updateclibot[bot], [dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot), [updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) and updatecli\r\n\r\n## Sponsors\r\n\r\nIf Updatecli is useful to you, please consider sponsoring it.  \r\nYour support helps maintain and improve this project.\r\n\r\n[![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/updatecli/updatecli?style=for-the-badge)](https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/stargazers) [![Sponsor](https://img.shields.io/badge/Sponsor-%E2%9D%A4-pink?style=for-the-badge)](https://www.updatecli.io/support/#sponsor-or-donate)",
    "DescriptionHTML": "\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-alert markdown-alert-warning\"\u003e\u003cp class=\"markdown-alert-title\"\u003e\u003csvg data-component=\"Octicon\" class=\"octicon octicon-alert mr-2\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M6.457 1.047c.659-1.234 2.427-1.234 3.086 0l6.082 11.378A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.082 15H1.918a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.543-2.575Zm1.763.707a.25.25 0 0 0-.44 0L1.698 13.132a.25.25 0 0 0 .22.368h12.164a.25.25 0 0 0 .22-.368Zm.53 3.996v2.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0v-2.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0ZM9 11a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003eWarning\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWarning this release introduces a regression that break cli autocompletion.\u003cbr\u003e\nMore information on \u003ca class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4562556383\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/issues/9028\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/updatecli/updatecli/issues/9028/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/issues/9028\"\u003e#9028\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFixed in \u003ca href=\"https://www.updatecli.io/changelogs/updatecli/changelogs/v0.118.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ev0.118.0\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eChanges\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e🐛 Bug Fixes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003efix(autodiscovery/kubernetes): handle empty yaml \u003ca class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/olblak/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/olblak\"\u003e@olblak\u003c/a\u003e (\u003ca class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4479309995\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/updatecli/updatecli/